{"id": "art-1444", "label": "Art. 1444", "title": "Art. 1444", "slug": "art-1444", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1365314097\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2167\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1365314097\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 144<sup>4</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_906529280\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2166\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_906529280\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Este\ninterzis&#259; creditarea de c&#259;tre societate a administratorilor acesteia,\nprin intermediul unor <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span> precum:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_678744092\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2165\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_678744092\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)acordarea de împrumuturi administratorilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1012215333\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2164\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1012215333\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)acordarea de avantaje financiare administratorilor cu\nocazia sau ulterior încheierii de c&#259;tre societate cu <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span> de livrare de bunuri,\nprest&#259;ri de servicii sau executare de lucr&#259;ri;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_964696040\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2163\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_964696040\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)garantarea direct&#259; ori indirect&#259;, în tot sau în\nparte, a oric&#259;ror împrumuturi acordate administratorilor,\nconcomitent&#259; ori ulterioar&#259; acord&#259;rii împrumutului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2004242456\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2162\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2004242456\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)garantarea direct&#259; ori indirect&#259;, în tot sau în\nparte, a execut&#259;rii de c&#259;tre administratori a oric&#259;ror alte <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span> personale ale acestora <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;e</span> persoane;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_583454662\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2161\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_583454662\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)dobândirea cu titlu oneros ori plata, în tot sau în\nparte, a unei <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;e</span> ce are drept obiect un\nîmprumut acordat de o <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;&#259;</span> persoan&#259;\nadministratorilor ori o alt&#259; <span class=SpellE>presta&#355;ie</span>\npersonal&#259; a acestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1022337124\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2160\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1022337124\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prevederile alin. (1) sunt aplicabile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunilor</span> în\ncare sunt <span class=SpellE>interesa&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>so&#355;ul</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>so&#355;ia</span>, rudele ori afinii pân&#259; la gradul\nal IV-lea inclusiv ai administratorului; de asemenea, dac&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span> <span class=SpellE>prive&#351;te</span> o\nsocietate la care una dintre persoanele anterior <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionate</span>\neste administrator ori <span class=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span>, singur&#259; sau\nîmpreun&#259; cu una dintre persoanele sus-<span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionate</span>,\no cot&#259; de cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 20% din valoarea\ncapitalului social subscris.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_665059948\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2159\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_665059948\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Prevederile alin.\n(1) nu se aplic&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_3303316\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2158\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_3303316\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)în cazul <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunilor</span> a\nc&#259;ror valoare exigibil&#259; cumulat&#259; este inferioar&#259;\nechivalentului în lei al sumei de 5.000 de euro;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_606465573\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2157\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_606465573\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în cazul în care <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span>\neste încheiat&#259; de societate în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nexercit&#259;rii curente a <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsale, iar clauzele <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunii</span> nu sunt mai\nfavorabile persoanelor prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n(2) decât cele pe care, în mod <span class=SpellE>obi&#351;nuit</span>,\nsocietatea le practic&#259; <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>ter&#355;e</span> persoane.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}